com.complexible.common.io
Interface PagedFile

All Superinterfaces:
Flushable
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractPagedFile
public interface PagedFile
extends Flushable

A PagedFile splits an IOFile into fixed-sized sections called Pages. Each Page gets a serial number, corresponding to its position in the PagedFile.

Since:
0.3
Version:
0.3
Author:
Pedro Oliveira
